{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Ocean_Planet_Steam_Page_Gif_1.gif?t=1736729337\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ocean Planet takes gameplay style inspired by 'Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy'\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 to the extreme with a higher focus on atmospheric &amp; immersive visuals, gameplay\u00a0 progression, hypnotic ambience, and a VERY lengthy main game map.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Bar_12+_OCEAN-THEMED_SECTIONS.png?t=1736729337\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Jump and climb your way through the atmospheric and immersive main game mode featuring over 12 ocean-themed sections including:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Octopus Base, Power Plant, Bubble Park, Pool Party, Beach, Shipwreck, Skull Sanctuary, Pirate Base, Aquarium, Seafood Palace, Outerspace, Spaceship, and Cockpit.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Ocean_Planet_Steam_Page_Gif_4.gif?t=1736729337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Bar_CHALLENGE_MODE.png?t=1736729337\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Test your skills in the Challenge Mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>These are platforming levels that break away from the Foddian style of the main game. The starting levels show off mechanics introduced in the main game, and find different uses of them. The later challenges become increasingly difficult.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Ocean_Planet_Steam_Page_Gif_5.gif?t=1736729337\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Bar_LEADERBOARDS___RANKINGS.png?t=1736729337\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Speedrun through the main game to achieve the fastest completion time!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>There are two separate leaderboards: one for the best overall time, which includes both the main game and all challenge levels, and another for the most wins, which ranks players based on the highest number of wins in the main game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2985740/extras/Ocean_Planet_Steam_Page_Gif_7.png?t=1736729337\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ascended","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/534fe7135399a8e055821604685084e73165cadf.jpg"},{"name":"Ascended 50 Times!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/ed334a1b1a9530dd6059bb8b1a880a2c852b2eac.jpg"},{"name":"Challenge Mode","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/e8f472e689ee37e42746bd815635169c3fb72b4c.jpg"},{"name":"Challenge Star!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/4a529c130079b9752cb0c51c0a9a40493c423d49.jpg"},{"name":"Leaderboards","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/3d6ed1d9a232e39f10f4bbb78b47b3f18ca4a6ec.jpg"},{"name":"A-Rank","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2985740/0bd944d87e55d35952827921deaeb0f15a1b081a.jpg"},{"name":" \tS-Rank!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pu